107
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:32,690
the coin jumped up in

108
00:04:32,690 --> 00:04:34,940
the air and randomly flipped itself.

109
00:04:35,260 --> 00:04:36,780
We know that doesn't happen,

110
00:04:36,780 --> 00:04:38,870
and we can measure the state

111
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:40,960
of the coin gently without changing it.

112
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:43,700
Quantum mechanics,

113
00:04:43,700 --> 00:04:44,860
not so clear.

114
00:04:44,980 --> 00:04:45,280
Well,

115
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:45,840
it is clear.

116
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,300
It's clear that that cannot be done.

117
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:48,240
Okay,

118
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:48,800
but let's,

119
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,020
we're going to talk a little bit.

