00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:52,740
Before we move on to more about vector space,

121
00:04:52,780 --> 00:04:53,680
and operators,

122
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,960
and the mathematics of quantum theory,

123
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,740
I want to talk a little

124
00:04:57,740 --> 00:04:58,800
more about the logic of it,

125
00:04:58,880 --> 00:05:01,820
and what way logic in quantum mechanics

126
00:05:01,820 --> 00:05:04,760
is different than logic in classical physics.

127
00:05:06,860 --> 00:05:09,380
Let's go back to our spin and our apparatus.

128
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,380
The spin is a,

