132
00:05:22,780 --> 00:05:24,080
We have to draw it on a blackboard,

133
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:25,900
and anything I draw on the blackboard will be classical.

134
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:29,100
Just because ink and pens are classical,

135
00:05:29,100 --> 00:05:31,920
or approximately classical.

136
00:05:32,180 --> 00:05:33,060
And an apparatus.

137
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:35,750
The apparatus is a window that has

