00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:18,340
And when the apparatus appears with

181
00:07:18,340 --> 00:07:20,640
a plus one sign in it,

182
00:07:21,060 --> 00:07:21,540
we'll say,

183
00:07:21,540 --> 00:07:21,860
uh-huh,

184
00:07:21,860 --> 00:07:22,820
