185
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:26,070
If we do it again with the same apparatus

186
00:07:26,070 --> 00:07:28,340
pointing in the same direction with the same spin,

187
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:29,880
we'll get up again,

188
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:30,760
and up again,

189
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:31,260
and up again.

190
00:07:31,340 --> 00:07:31,900
In that sense,

191
00:07:31,900 --> 00:07:36,940
