195
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,440
So things are not that weird.

196
00:07:50,060 --> 00:07:51,320
And that's awfully important,

197
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:54,070
because we have to have some

198
00:07:54,070 --> 00:07:56,380
