199
00:07:56,380 --> 00:07:58,520
in order to make any sense out of things.

200
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,040
So this is a good thing.

201
00:08:00,700 --> 00:08:01,800
When you measure something,

202
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:03,300
and you measure it again and again and again,

203
00:08:03,380 --> 00:08:04,080
you get the same answer.

204
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:04,560
Yeah?

205
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:05,850
So how does that fit

