00:10:51,040 --> 00:10:53,760
and we measure the same procedure.

285
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:57,380
We measure something that we can now call sigma x.

286
00:10:59,160 --> 00:11:02,040
And sigma x is always plus or minus one.

287
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:04,390
And the same thing if we turn

288
00:11:04,390 --> 00:11:06,480
the apparatus around so that it's facing frontward.

289
00:11:06,540 --> 00:11:06,860
In fact,

290
00:11:06,860 --> 00:11:09,200
