292
00:11:14,020 --> 00:11:15,480
This would be a little bit strange,

293
00:11:15,580 --> 00:11:16,420
more than a little bit,

294
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:21,120
if this object really were a classical vector,

295
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:22,080
a little vector,

296
00:11:22,420 --> 00:11:24,200
perhaps a vector of unit length.

297
00:11:24,820 --> 00:11:26,940
If it were a vector of unit length,

298
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:29,250
