330
00:12:36,180 --> 00:12:37,850
You could do the experiment

331
00:12:37,850 --> 00:12:39,520
over and over and over again.

332
00:12:40,620 --> 00:12:42,560
Half the times you would

333
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:44,500
