00:21:06,820 --> 00:21:08,540
that you didn't rotate it at all,

560
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:10,780
what is N dot M in that case?

561
00:21:13,220 --> 00:21:13,580
One.

562
00:21:14,420 --> 00:21:14,780
Alright.

563
00:21:15,260 --> 00:21:16,640
And that would just be an indication

564
00:21:17,960 --> 00:21:20,660
that you got the same answer if N was up,

565
00:21:20,820 --> 00:21:22,200
and you did the experiment,

566
00:21:22,320 --> 00:21:23,440
you'd get it up and up and up

567
00:21:23,440 --> 00:21:24,460
over and over and over again.

568
00:21:24,700 --> 00:21:25,400
Okay.

